<view class="page" >
 <!--页头-->
 <view id='ppt'>
 <image src='cloud://anglfs-5f307e.616e-anglfs-5f307e/logo.jpg'></image></view>
 <view class="page__hd">
  <view class="head">
    <input    type="text" name='start'  bindtap='city' value='{{city1}}'/>
    <image src="/images/to.png" class="to"></image>
    <input bindtap='city1' time value='{{city}}' auto-focus/>
  </view>
 </view>

<view class='time'>
      <view class='picker'>
       <image src="/images/date.png" class="dateImg"></image>
      <view>
          <picker mode="multiSelector" value="{{dateTime}}" bindchange="changeDateTime" bindcolumnchange="changeDateTimeColumn" range="{{dateTimeArray}}">
          日期: {{dateTimeArray[0][dateTime[0]]}}-{{dateTimeArray[1][dateTime[1]]}}-{{dateTimeArray[2][dateTime[2]]}}
      </picker>
      </view>
      </view> 
</view>

<view class='time'>
      <view class='picker'>
        <image src="/images/date.png" class="dateImg"></image>
        <view>
          <picker mode="multiSelector" value="{{dateTime1}}" bindchange="changeDateTime1" bindcolumnchange="" range="{{dateTimeArray}}">
        直至: {{dateTimeArray1[0][dateTime1[0]]}}-{{dateTimeArray1[1][dateTime1[1]]}}-{{dateTimeArray1[2][dateTime1[2]]}}
    </picker>
        </view>
      </view> 
</view>


<view class='time'>
      <view class='picker'>
      <image src="/images/Tourist.png" class="dateImg"></image>
         <picker bindchange="bindPickerChange" value="{{index}}" range="{{array}}">
    <view class="picker">
      人数：{{array[index]}}
    </view>
  </picker>
      </view> 
</view>

<view class='time'>
      <view class='picker'>
      <image src="/images/money.jpg" class="dateImg"></image>
           <input  name="beizhu" value='备注：'/>
            
      </view>   
</view>

<view class='time'>
<image src="/images/vehicle.png" class="dateImg"></image>

  <checkbox-group class="radio-group" 
          >
  <label class="radio">
    <checkbox value='人找车' bindtap='ppl' />人找车
    <checkbox value='车找人' bindtap='ppl1' />车找人
   
  </label>
</checkbox-group>
</view>

<view class="page__bd">
       <button  class='search' bindtap='open'>搜索</button>
</view>
</view>
